data.description: Presenting an exceptional opportunity to own this 3-bedroom, 2-bath residence centrally located in the heart of Modesto! This well-appointed home offers a unique combination of comfort and convenience, with close proximity to schools, parks, and walking trails. Upon entry, you are greeted by a formal living room adorned with an elegant fireplace, setting the stage for intimate gatherings and cozy evenings. The heart of this home is the spacious family room that seamlessly transitions to the backyard, where you'll discover a large backyard with ample patio space, and a built-in pool! This outdoor oasis is perfect for relaxation and entertainment, making it the focal point of your leisure activities. Three well-appointed bedrooms offer comfortable living spaces, while two tastefully designed bathrooms provide convenience for the entire household. The proximity to nearby parks and trails beckon for outdoor adventures. Whether you're into hiking, biking, or simply enjoying the great outdoors, you'll find plenty of options to explore right at your doorstep. This property offers a rare opportunity to enjoy a comfortable and vibrant living experience. Don't miss your chance to make this exceptional house your forever home!
